{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/1944","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/1944/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/1944/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/1944/events","html_url":"https://github.com/pugjs/pug/issues/1944","id":73776996,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3Mzc3Njk5Ng==","number":1944,"title":"Unbuffered comments can break indented blocks...","user":{"login":"flynx","id":3821,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM4MjE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3821?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx","html_url":"https://github.com/flynx","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/flynx/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":1,"created_at":"2015-05-07T00:09:18Z","updated_at":"2015-08-14T23:50:41Z","closed_at":"2015-08-14T23:50:41Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"**Here is a simple example:**\n\n``` jade\nif 123\n  div some text...\n//- comment documenting the else branch...\nelse\n  span some other text...\n```\n\n**Result:** this code breaks with the following error pointing to the else keyword:\n\n```\nUnexpected else without if\n```\n\n**Expected behavior:** unbuffered comments should not affect block handling...\n\n**A bit of motivation:** unbuffered comments are mostly used to document the actual template and are neither needed nor rendered in the HTML, thus should behave as traditional comments (no-op elements) and be simply ignored and dropped by the lexer/translator.\n\n_BTW, this is not an issue for normal \"comments\" as they translate to HTML comments and their indent is significant and indicates their position in the resulting tree._\n\nThanks!\n","closed_by":{"login":"TimothyGu","id":1538624,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjE1Mzg2MjQ=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1538624?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu","html_url":"https://github.com/TimothyGu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/TimothyGu/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/1944/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/pugjs/pug/issues/1944/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}